{"tid":854865,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"合約員工懷孕後不獲續約   職工盟：應修例視作解僱可向僱主追討賠償","createTime":"2018-10-09T16:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T13:55:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7c8bd689c1fccea0cc2d13cb749bd99e4fde7c22","tid":854865,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:08:34.000Z","msg":"職工盟較早前接獲求助，一名於物流公司任職逾10年的員工懷孕後不獲續約，才得悉不視為解僱，無法向僱主追討賠償。<br />\n<br />\n事主周女士說，懷孕時任物流業務總負責人，仍有上班，至去年11月身體不適留院，公司即以「業務縮減」為由不續約，但公司有招聘同一職位。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，施政報告將公布將產假增加至14周。職工盟表示歡迎，但指出合約僱員懷孕不受僱傭條例保障，要求政府修例堵塞漏洞。"},{"pid":"5236f06777e2126ed0a215d4f460077098e16c77","tid":854865,"uid":54264,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:10:16.000Z","msg":"咁男人呢"},{"pid":"4709cf190458a54e0c0b7e179bfc5ab885241b78","tid":854865,"uid":2429,"like":19,"dislike":6,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:12:57.000Z","msg":"以後女人自動續約呀笨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6039b93a67a69cdc3d56067a890d091fc4c5daa3","tid":854865,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":11,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"4709cf190458a54e0c0b7e179bfc5ab885241b78","tid":854865,"uid":2429,"like":19,"dislike":6,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:12:57.000Z","msg":"以後女人自動續約呀笨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:14:37.000Z","msg":"合約女員工有左, 強制僱主續約 + 前四後六比人工, 否則合約工都可以去勞工處告鳩腦細<br />\n<br />\n有閪真係大N晒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52db0c041b52ca44930f3b16b15a5518a66c56a2","tid":854865,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:16:43.000Z","msg":"假設俾足產假人工<br />\n成件事其實合情合理合法<br />\n完約唔要佢有咩好拗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" cl